Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: One White Raven stance.
Specifics: When you are in a White Raven stance and adjacent to at least one ally, you gain a +1 bonus to AC. Furthermore, when you are wielding one of the White Raven discipline's preferred weapons, each ally adjacent to you gains a +1 bonus to AC. These bonuses don’t apply when you’re flat-footed.

Use: Automatic.